Package: baRcodeR
Title: Custom R Tools for Collection, Tracking, and Curation of Biological Samples using 2D Barcodes
Version: 0.0.2.0000
Authors@R: c(person("Yihan", "Wu", role="aut", email = "yihan.wu@queensu.ca"), person("Robert", "Colautti", email = "robert.colautti@queensu.ca", role = c("aut", "cre")), 
    person("Emily", "Bao", role="aut"))
Maintainer: Robert Colautti <robert.colautti@queensu.ca>
Description: Tools to create labels for biological samples. The creation of 
    labels and pdf files for printing on sticker sheets is guided by user 
    prompts. Both one-level and hierarchical labels can be created. 
Depends: 
    R (>= 3.4.0),
    qrcode
